channel.title: Omfg help me i have my server running but i cant see window!
channel.description: I have my server running. but i cant see the cmd window! and when i try to click run, it says 43594 is already in use...idk where i can find the window thats running already...help me please!

item.title: Omfg help me i have my server running but i cant see window!
item.dc:creator: @Hackerz Hackerz
item.description:
@Hackerz wrote:

Theres a chance that you installed another program that uses that port number. Try changing the port number if that doesn’t work then you have something that is making your server run or just every port is being used by something else. kinda like a installed server, limewire, bitcomet. Things like that may be using that port
